Required scope: &lt;code&gt;social&lt;/code&gt;

Create a game binary record.
&lt;p&gt;Other detail info:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;code&gt;key&lt;/code&gt; should follow these rules:
1. support uppercase and lowercase letters, numbers, and separators &lt;b&gt;&#34;-&#34;&lt;/b&gt;, &lt;b&gt;&#34;_&#34;&lt;/b&gt;, &lt;b&gt;&#34;.&#34;&lt;/b&gt; are allowed  
2. begin and end with letters or numbers
3. spaces are not allowed
4. separators must not appears twice in a row


Supported file types: jpeg, jpg, png, bmp, gif, mp3, webp, and bin.

