	CLIENT: record can be modified by client and server.

&lt;b&gt;Request Body Example:&lt;/b&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;
	{
		&#34;__META&#34;: {
			&#34;set_by&#34;: &#34;SERVER&#34;
		}
		...
	}
&lt;/pre&gt;

